data.description: Majestic house located in highly desired Stone Oak area, and one of the best school district in SA, NEISD, with half acre lot, front yard to the cul-de-sac, and backyard to Hardy Oak Elementary School! This rare find features granite counter top, wood/tile floor downstairs, extra room upstairs, build-in shelves, over-sized garage, plus security/sounds/sprinkler system, and recent AC unit (one of two), recent paint throughout the house (expect guest room & bathrooms), and walkway leads to backyard circular patio and shed! Book a private tour and make this wonderful property yours!
